org.kepler.module.gui

Class Initialize

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kepler.module.gui.Initialize
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<KeplerGraphFrameUpdater>, KeplerGraphFrameUpdater, ModuleInitializer

    public class Initialize
extends java.lang.Object
implements KeplerGraphFrameUpdater, ModuleInitializer
    Perform initialization for the GUI module. This class implements KeplerGraphFrameUpdater so that it can add a view selector to the toolbar. Additionally, it initializes the moml filters for actors in the util module.
    Author:
    Daniel Crawl
